- space in xslt: &#160; (https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1461649/how-to-insert-nbsp-in-xslt)
- space in xslt: <xsl:text> </xsl:text> (https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1461649/how-to-insert-nbsp-in-xslt)
- margin for buttons: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26962837/putting-margins-between-buttons
- using FO in xampp (https://community.apachefriends.org/f/viewtopic.php?f=16&t=48602):
    - Open \xampp\php\php.ini file in your text editor
    - Add (without semicolon at the beginning => otherwise it is a comment):
        extension=php_xmlrpc.dll
        extension=php_xsl.dll
